  sync. Top-level `RELEASING.md` is NOT under `docs/plans/`, so it is never
  scanned — zero false-positive risk. (`docs/RELEASE.md` would also be outside
  the scan, but top-level is the stronger convention signal.)
- Convention: top-level `RELEASING.md` sits naturally beside `CHANGELOG.md` and
